cz.syntea.xdef

Interface XDValue

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<XDValue>, XDValueID
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    XDBNFGrammar, XDBNFRule, XDBytes, XDContainer, XDDatetime, XDDocument, XDDuration, XDElement, XDException, XDInput, XDNamedValue, XDOutput, XDParser, XDParseResult, XDRegex, XDRegexResult, XDReport, XDResultSet, XDService, XDStatement, XDXmlOutStream, XDXQueryExpr, XXData, XXDocument, XXElement, XXNode, XXSelector
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    XDElementAbstract, XDParserAbstract, XDResultSetAbstract, XDValueAbstract

    public interface XDValue
extends java.lang.Comparable<XDValue>, XDValueID
    Provides the interface for usage of internal objects of x-script. This interface provides general access methods to values of variables and of parameters of methods in X-definitions.
